    "Details": "First built in 3086, the ND-RR4 is built around an Ultra AC/20 as the entire design philosophy. A Targeting Computer sharpens the main gun and all supporting weapons simultaneously. Two ER Medium Lasers and two Medium Pulse Lasers provide layered backup across multiple ranges. Four tons of CASE-protected ammunition gives the pilot sustained firepower. Jump jets were dropped in this variant to free tonnage for the heavier loadout.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.11</color></b>",
